features: Versatile Oven Rack Puller:Our oven rack puller effortlessly removes or pushes oven racks with its beautifully designed slots, accommodating various oven rack shapes.
Safe and Convenient: With a generous length of 28cm/11 inches, the oven rack puller keeps your hands and arms safely away from hot oven racks, preventing burns.
Durable and Sturdy: With a thickness of 1cm/0.4 inches, our wooden rack puller is built to last and won't break easily. And the wooden material can withstand high temperatures.
Smooth and Splinter-Free: The polished surface of the beech wood oven rack puller ensures a smooth, splinter-free grip for comfortable and secure handling.
Easy Storage: When not in use, simply store the oven rack push pull tool in a dry place away from water, ensuring its longevity.
body.description: Thanks to its 1cm/0.4-inch thickness, this oven rack push pull tool is sturdy and reliable, ensuring it won't break during use. The wooden material also enables it to withstand high temperatures. Safety is a top priority, which is why our wooden rack puller features a long handle measuring 28cm/11 inches. This generous length keeps your hands and arms away from hot oven racks, minimizing the risk of burns. With its polished surface, this oven rack puller provides a smooth and splinter-free grip. The beautifully designed slots at both ends accommodate various oven rack shapes, allowing for easy maneuverability.
